I am Contego Caelestis, cleric of the 52nd season. I have read your rules and understand them very well. I have known Callandre since I was a very young cleric, she has been a mentor and friend throughout the game. We met many moons ago in North Karana while trying to finish a part of her quest for her other character and since then I have kept in touch with her. I have seen her fly through all her 50+ levels. Congratulations again!!!<br>
<br>
